adams.flow.control.Flow
	-annotation
	This flow shows how to determine the column index of\ncolumns which name matches a user-specified reguarl\nexpression.
	-actor
		adams.flow.source.FileSupplier
			-file
			${EXAMPLE_FLOWS}/data/iris.csv
	-actor
		adams.flow.transformer.SpreadSheetFileReader
			-reader
				adams.data.io.input.CsvSpreadSheetReader
					-spreadsheet-type
						adams.data.spreadsheet.SpreadSheet
	-actor
		adams.flow.transformer.SpreadSheetGetColumnIndex
			-column-name
			sepal.*
	-actor
		adams.flow.sink.Display
	-flow-execution-listener
		adams.flow.execution.NullListener

